============================================================
API RESPONSE FORMAT
============================================================

All endpoints must use standard response shape:

Success:

{
  "ok": true,
  "data": {},
  "error": null,
  "timestamp": "ISO_DATE"
}

Error:

{
  "ok": false,
  "data": null,
  "error": {
    "code": "ERROR_CODE",
    "message": "Human readable message"
  },
  "timestamp": "ISO_DATE"
}

Required error codes:

- ENTERPRISE_OS_DISABLED
- CAPABILITY_NOT_FOUND
- OPERATING_CADENCE_NOT_FOUND
- ENTERPRISE_STATE_NOT_FOUND
- SELF_EVOLUTION_DISABLED
- SELF_EVOLUTION_PROPOSAL_ONLY
- IMPROVEMENT_PROPOSAL_NOT_FOUND
- EVOLUTION_SAFETY_BLOCKED
- ARCHITECTURE_DRIFT_SCAN_FAILED
- TECH_DEBT_SCAN_FAILED
- API_EVOLUTION_BLOCKED
- SCHEMA_EVOLUTION_BLOCKED
- GOVERNANCE_REFINEMENT_DISABLED
- POLICY_MATURITY_FAILED
- GOVERNANCE_DRIFT_DETECTED
- POLICY_SIMULATION_BLOCKED
- CONTROL_IMPACT_FAILED
- RISK_APPETITE_INVALID
- LONG_HORIZON_DISABLED
- TREND_SIGNAL_NOT_FOUND
- STRATEGIC_THESIS_NOT_FOUND
- LONG_RANGE_SCENARIO_FAILED
- ADVANTAGE_ANALYSIS_FAILED
- MOAT_ASSESSMENT_FAILED
- LESSONS_MEMORY_DISABLED
- LESSON_NOT_FOUND
- LESSON_REDACTION_REQUIRED
- ADVISORY_ONLY_ACTION
- TENANT_ACCESS_DENIED

